Package: wickradarwin
Type: Package
Title: Evolutionary Strategy Search over Wickra Strategy Specs
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-darwin over its C ABI hub: a seeded EvolveSpec
    drives a byte-identical genetic search over Wickra strategy specs - the same
    protocol as the CLI and every other binding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-darwin
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-darwin/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-darwin C ABI shared library (WKDARWIN_LIB)
    and its header (WKDARWIN_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
